-- Al Hokair Group to Raise Egypt Investments, al-Madina Reports
-- B y   G l e n   C a r e y
-- 2012-10-15T07:31:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-15/al-hokair-group-to-raise-egypt-investments-al-madina-reports.html
Al Hokair Group , a Saudi
entertainment and leisure company, plans to raise its
investments in  Egypt  as the political situation stabilizes,  al-
Madina  said, citing General Manager Ziad Maghrebiyeh.  The investments will include five commercial centers around
the cities of Cairo and Alexandria, the newspaper said.  Al Hokair will have a total of 3.5 billion Egyptian pounds
($570 million) invested in Egypt, newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Glen Carey in Riyadh at 
 gcarey8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  